==Text==
''The words of wisdom left here by the Lord Ravager known as "Phantylia":''<br /><div align="center">Hehe, I know you can see me. Go on, guess. What do you think I'm hoping to witness here?<br />
A genius's mind, destroyed by its own creator?<br />
A hollow Scepter, catching the glance from a new god?<br />
A newborn Overlord, bestowing the glorious flames of ruin upon the cosmos?<br />
Oh, the drama!<br />
But no, that's not quite it. Or rather, that's not all I care about.<br />
Does the coronation or downfall of a fellow Lord truly matter so much?<br />
What I'm hoping for from all this "Trailblazing" is one... grand... show.<br />
The universe, in all its forms, is just a play. And a play needs its twists and turns to have any real flavor, don't you think?</div>

